🎤Lyrics: Céline Dion - I Love You

[Intro]
I must be crazy now
Maybe I dream too much
But when I think of you
I long to feel your touch

To whisper in your ear
Words that are old as time
Words only you would hear
If only you were mine

And I'd whisper these words as you'd lie here by my side

[Chorus]
I love you, please say
You love me too, these three words
They could change our lives forever
And I promise you that we will always be together
Till the end of time

So today, I finally find the courage deep inside
Just to walk right up to your door
But my body can't move when I finally get to it
Just like a thousand times before
Then without a word he handed me this letter
Read I hope this finds the way into your heart, it said

[Chorus]
I love you, please say
You love me too, these three words
They could change our lives forever
And I promise you that we will always be together
Till the end of time

[Verse 3]
Well maybe I, I need a little love yeah
And maybe I, I need a little care
And maybe I, maybe you, maybe you, maybe you
Oh you need somebody just to hold you
If you do, just reach out and I'll be there

[Chorus]
I love you, please say
You love me too, these three words
They could change our lives forever
And I promise you that we will always be together
Till the end of time

[Outro]
These three words
They could change our lives forever
And I promise you that we will always be together
Oh, I love you
Please say you love me too
Please please
Say you love me too
Till the end of time
My baby
Together, together, forever
Till the end of time
I love you
I will be your light
Shining bright
Shining through your eyes
My baby

🎤 Lyrics:  Gigi Perez - Sailor Song

[Verse 1]
I saw her in the rightest way
Looking like Anne Hathaway
Laughing while she hit her pen and coughed, and coughed
And then she came up to my knees
Begging, "Baby, would you please
Do the things you said you'd do to me, to me?"

[Chorus]
Oh, won't you kiss me on the mouth and love me like a sailor?
And when you get a taste, can you tell me, what's my flavor?
I don't believe in God, but I believe that you're my savior
My mom says that she's worried, but I'm covered in this favor
And when we're getting dirty, I forget all that is wrong
I sleep so I can see you 'cause I hate to wait so long
I sleep so I can see you, and I hate to wait so long

[Verse 2]
She took my fingers to her mouth
The kind of thing that makes you proud
That nothing else had ever worked out, worked out
And lately, I tried other things
But nothing can capture the sting
Of the venom she's gonna spit out right now

[Chorus]
Oh, won't you kiss me on the mouth and love me like a sailor?
And when you get a taste, can you tell me, what's my flavor?
I don't believe in God, but I believe that you're my savior
I know that you've been worried, but you're dripping in my favor
And when we're getting dirty, I forget all that is wrong
I sleep so I can see you 'cause I hate to wait so long
I sleep so I can see you, and I hate to wait so long

[Outro]
And we can run away to the walls inside your house
I can be the cat, baby, you can be the mouse
And we can laugh off things that we know nothing about
We can go forever until you wanna sit it out

snippet.title: Ari Lasso [Full Album Terbaik] Lagu Pop Nostalgia Tahun 90an Hits Sampai Saat Ini
snippet.description:
Ari Lasso [Full Album Terbaik] Lagu Pop Nostalgia Tahun 90an Hits Sampai Saat Ini           

-------------------------------------------------------------
Selamat datang di saluran musik kami
Kami bangga mempersembahkan kepada Anda kekayaan musik yang kaya dan beragam, yang terus diperbarui untuk memenuhi semua preferensi musik Anda. Baik Anda mencari lagu hits terbaru, lagu klasik, atau lagu yang tidak jelas namun bernilai, saluran kami memiliki semuanya.

Dewa 19:
Gaya: Dewa 19 adalah salah satu band rock paling terkenal di Indonesia. Musik mereka menggabungkan rock, pop, dan rock progresif.
Penampilan: Band ini terkenal dengan melodinya yang kuat, lirik yang dalam, dan teknik bermain yang terampil. Lagu-lagu mereka seringkali membawa pesan bermakna tentang kehidupan, cinta, dan masyarakat.

Ari Lasso: Penyanyi terkenal Indonesia, terutama menyanyikan musik pop dan rock. Sebelum memulai karir solo, ia adalah anggota band Dewa 19, salah satu band rock paling terkenal di Indonesia. Dalam karir solonya, Ari Lasso terus mengembangkan gaya musik pop rocknya dan menjadi salah satu artis papan atas Indonesia.

Selain itu di channel kami selalu membuat banyak konten musik yang bagus dan menarik
Bergabunglah bersama kami untuk menjelajahi dunia musik tanpa batas, nikmati momen relaksasi yang indah, dan temukan melodi yang menyentuh hati Anda. Jangan lupa untuk menekan tombol ikuti agar Anda tidak ketinggalan video apa pun dan bergabunglah dengan kami dalam berbagi semangat kami terhadap musik kepada semua orang!

Terima kasih karena selalu mendukung dan mendampingi kami. Semoga Anda mendapatkan momen bahagia dan bermakna dalam mendengarkan musik!

snippet.description:
Official Music Video Lagu Terbaru Fauzana 

Music Credits:
Artist: Fauzana
Title: Bapindah Ka Nan Lain

Arr : Decky Ryan
Video Maker : PNg Video
©2025 Fauzana Official

Make up By : Pelaminan 3 Putri Umi 
Dress By : Hilman Samudera 

♪ Lirik ♪

Samulo denai indak picayo (Awalnya aku ga percaya)
Uda Bapindah Ka Lain Hati (Kamu berpindah ke lain hati)
Denai cubo sadarkan diri (Kucoba untuk sadar diri)
Denai cubo ikhlaskan hati (Kucoba untuk ikhlaskan hati)
Mungkin iko jalan ilahi (Mungkin ini jalan ilahi)

Sairiang sasalan di hari (Seiring penyelasan)
Lah denai cubo lupokan luko di hati (Sudah ku coba untuk melupakan luka di hati)
Kini uda datang manyasali (Sekarang kamu datang untuk menyesali)
dek uda lah bapindah hati (Karena kamu sudah berpindah hati)
ka nan lain (Ke yang lain)

Jikok kato maaf ka denai bari (Jika kata maaf akan kuberi)
Jikok pinto hati nan ka uda pintak (Jika hati ini yang kamu mau)
Hatiko lah tatutuik untuak uda surang (Maaf, hati ini sudah tertutup untuk kamu seorang)
bia nan lain nan datang (Biarkan yang lain yang datang)

jan di undang juo cinto nan lah lamo mati (Jangan di undang lagi cinta yang telah lama mati)
jan di ungkik juo kisah nan lah lamo hilang (Jangan diungkit lagi kisah yang sudah lama hilang)
kini denai nio surang (Kini aku mau sendiri)
Manjalani hiduik jo hati tanang (Menjalani hidup dengan tenang)
